headline: AutoZone Gears Up to Report Q2 Earnings: What to Expect?
summary: AZO heads into Q2 earnings with EPS seen down 2.5% despite 8.8% sales growth, as rising capex and SG&A weigh on margins.

headline: Evercore ISI Group Maintains Outperform on AutoZone, Raises Price Target to $4125
summary: Evercore ISI Group  analyst Greg Melich   maintains AutoZone (NYSE:AZO) with a Outperform and raises the price target from $4100 to $4125.
